content:
[[module CSS]]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat+Alternates&display=swap');
h1, #page-title {
    color: #000;
}

#side-bar a:visited {
    color: #051b73
}

div#container-wrap {
    background: url(https://files.scpfoundation.net/local--files/theme:loneliness-and-oblivion/body_bg-gok.png) top left repeat-x;
}

#header h1 a {
    color: #fff;
}
#header h1 a::before {
    color: #e9ebf0;
}
#header h2 span::before {
    color: #f2f2fd;
}
#header h2 span {
    text-shadow: 3px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
    color: #ffffff;
}



a {
    color: #051b73;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
}
a.newpage {
    color: #051b73;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
}



#top-bar ul li.sfhover a,
#top-bar ul li:hover a {
    background-color: #e3e3e3;
    color: #505050;
}
#top-bar ul li ul {
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

#top-bar ul li ul a, #top-bar a:hover {
    color: #505050;
}



#search-top-box-input {
    color: #FFF;
    background-color: #000;
}
#search-top-box-form input[type=submit] {
    color: #fff;
    background-color: #000;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #000,#000,#000);
}



.page-rate-widget-box .rate-points {
background-color: #616163 !important;
    border: solid 1px #616163;
}
.page-rate-widget-box .cancel {
    background-color: #616163;
    border: solid 1px #616163;
}
.page-rate-widget-box .cancel a {
    color: #fff;
}
.page-rate-widget-box .rateup a:hover, .page-rate-widget-box .ratedown a:hover {
    background: #616163;
}
.page-rate-widget-box .rateup, .page-rate-widget-box .ratedown {
    background-color: #e8dcd4;
    border-top: solid 1px #616163;
    border-bottom: solid 1px #616163;
}
.page-rate-widget-box .rateup a, .page-rate-widget-box .ratedown a {
    color: #000;
}

.page-rate-widget-box .cancel a:hover {
    background: #464646;
}



#side-bar div.menu-item img {
    filter: hue-rotate(0deg) brightness(0%);
}
#side-bar .side-block {
    border: 1px solid #000000;
    background: #fff !important;
}
.side-block{
background-color: #ffffff;
}
#side-bar .heading {
    color: #000;
}


body {
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'Montserrat Alternates', sans-serif;
}
[[/module]]

[[iftags +版式]]
在你的作品开头添加如下语法以应用此版式：
> @@[[include theme:loneliness-and-oblivion]]@@
[[/iftags]]
